          "name": "item_crellas_crozier",
          "name_loc": "Crella's Crozier",
          "desc_loc": "<h1>Active: Rite of Rumusque</h1> You enter ghost form for %duration% seconds, becoming immune to physical damage, but are unable to attack and %extra_spell_damage_percent%%% more vulnerable to magic damage.<br><br>Steal %movespeed_steal_pct%%% movement speed from enemy heroes in %active_radius% range every second. Movement speed steal lasts %stack_duration%s.<br><br>Putrefaction Aura's effect is increased to %active_health_steal%%%. All of the lost Health Restoration is redirected to you every second.\n\n<h1>Passive: Putrefaction Aura</h1>Reduces nearby enemy heroes' Health Restoration by %health_steal%%%.<br><br>Radius: %radius%",
